---
import PageLayout from '../layouts/PageLayout.astro';
---

<PageLayout title="About" description="Learn about OmniHex Lab and its content direction.">
	<section class="page">
		<h1>About OmniHex Lab</h1>
		<p>
			OmniHex Lab is a low-cost content site for AI news, explainers, tutorials, prompts, tools, and multilingual technology briefs.
		</p>
		<p>
			The site is built with Astro and Markdown, deployed to Cloudflare Pages, and designed to work without a database or image storage in the early stage. The content model is ready for RSS intake, source attribution, and future automated publishing workflows.
		</p>
	</section>
</PageLayout>
